Negara Malaysia (BNM)\"}],\" under the Financial Services Act 2013.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"When you proceed to payment, you will be redirected to Razorpay Curlec’s secure hosted payment page. By completing payment, you also agree to Razorpay Curlec’s Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.\"}],\"$Ld\"]}]]}],\"$Le\",\"$Lf\",\"$L10\",\"$L11\",\"$L12\",\"$L13\",\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\"]}],\"$L17\"]}]}],null,\"$L18\"]}],{},null,false]},null,false]},null,false],\"$L19\",false]],\"m\":\"$undefined\",\"G\":[\"$1a\",[]],\"s\":false,\"S\":true}\n1b:I[24431,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n1d:I[15278,[],\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\"]\n1f:I[24431,[],\"ViewportBoundary\"]\n21:I[24431,[],\"MetadataBoundary\"]\n22:\"$Sreact.suspense\"\nd:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg\",\"children\":\"Vault 6 Studios does not directly handle, process, or store any payment card data. All sensitive payment information is transmitted directly to Razorpay Curlec and subject to their PCI DSS-compliant infrastructure.\"}]\ne:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"2. Accepted Payment Methods\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The following payment methods are accepted at checkout, subject to availability via Razorpay Curlec’s gateway:\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-2\",\"children\":\"FPX Online Banking\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs mb-2\",\"children\":\"Direct bank transfer via Financial Process Exchange (FPX), available for all major Malaysian banks:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-500 text-xs columns-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Maybank2u\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"CIMB Clicks\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Public Bank\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"RHB Now\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Hong Leong Connect\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"AmBank\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Bank Islam\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Bank Rakyat\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"BSN\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"And others\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-2\",\"children\":\"Credit & Debit Cards\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs\",\"children\":\"Visa and Mastercard credit and debit cards are accepted. Cards must be enabled for online/international transactions. 3D Secure authentication may be required.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-2\",\"children\":\"E-Wallets\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs mb-2\",\"children\":\"Selected Malaysian e-wallets are supported, subject to Razorpay Curlec gateway availability:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-500 text-xs columns-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"GrabPay\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Touch ‘n Go eWallet\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Boost\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"ShopeePay\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 text-xs mt-2\",\"children\":\"Available e-wallet options are determined by HitPay and may change without prior notice.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg\",\"children\":\"We do not accept cash payments, bank transfers made outside the Razorpay Curlec checkout, or cryptocurrency. All payments must be completed via the Razorpay Curlec payment page presented at checkout.\"}]]}]]}]\nf:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"3. Currency & Pricing\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"All prices displayed on vault6studios.com are in \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"Malaysian Ringgit (MYR)\"}],\", inclusive of applicable taxes. The amount charged at checkout is the final MYR amount displayed.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"If you are paying with a card issued in a foreign currency, your card issuer will apply their prevailing exchange rate and any applicable foreign transaction fees. Vault 6 Studios is not responsible for exchange rate differences or foreign transaction charges imposed by your bank or card issuer.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Prices are subject to change at any time prior to order confirmation. The price applicable to your order is the price displayed at the time your payment is successfully processed.\"}]]}]]}]\n10:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"4. When Payment Is Charged\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Payment is charged \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"in full at the time of checkout\"}],\" for all order types, including:\"]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"Ready Stock orders\"}],\" — Full payment charged upon checkout. Order is fulfilled and dispatched within 1–2 business days.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"Pre-Order items\"}],\" — Full payment charged at the time of pre-order placement. Items are dispatched upon arrival from the manufacturer or distributor.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"A binding sale is formed only when Razorpay Curlec confirms successful payment and we dispatch a written order confirmation via WhatsApp or email, in accordance with Section 5 of our \",[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/terms\",\"className\":\"text-blue-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Terms & Conditions\"}],\".\"]}]]}]]}]\n11:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"5. Payment Security\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Vault 6 Studios and Razorpay Curlec implement the following security measures to protect your payment:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"PCI DSS Compliance:\"}],\" Razorpay Curlec is PCI DSS compliant. All card data is handled exclusively within their certified secure environment. We do not receive or store full card numbers, CVVs, or expiry dates.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"HTTPS Encryption:\"}],\" All data transmitted between your browser and our site, and between our site and Razorpay Curlec, is encrypted using TLS 1.2 or higher.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"3D Secure (3DS):\"}],\" Where supported, card payments may be subject to 3DS authentication (Verified by Visa / Mastercard SecureCode), adding an additional verification step via your card issuer.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"No Stored Card Data:\"}],\" We do not store any payment card information in our systems. Each transaction is processed independently through Razorpay Curlec.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs\",\"children\":\"If you suspect any fraudulent activity related to a transaction on our site, contact us immediately via WhatsApp and notify your bank or card issuer.\"}]]}]]}]\n12:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"6. Failed & Declined Payments\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"If your payment is declined or fails to process:\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"list-decimal list-inside space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"No order will be placed and no charge will be made to your account.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"You may attempt payment again using the same or a different payment method.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Common reasons for decline include insufficient funds, card restrictions on online transactions, incorrect card details, or issuer security holds.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"If you continue to experience issues, contact your bank or card issuer first, then contact us for assistance.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs\",\"children\":\"Vault 6 Studios is not liable for any charges imposed by your bank or card issuer in connection with failed payment attempts.\"}]]}]]}]\n13:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"7. Refund Processing\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Where a refund is approved under our \",[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/return-policy\",\"className\":\"text-blue-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Return & Refund Policy\"}],\" or due to a seller-initiated cancellation:\"]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"Refunds are processed via the \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"original payment method\"}],\" where possible.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"Refunds are initiated by us through Razorpay Curlec within the timeframe specified in our Return Policy (\",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"7–14 business days\"}],\" after approval).\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"The time for a refund to appear in your account depends on your bank or e-wallet provider and may take an additional 3–10 business days after we initiate the refund.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Original shipping fees are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Razorpay Curlec processing fees may be deducted from refunds where applicable — we will communicate this clearly before processing.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-xs\",\"children\":\"If you have not received your refund within the expected timeframe, please contact us with your order reference number for investigation.\"}]]}]]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"8. Chargebacks & Payment Disputes\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We take payment integrity seriously. If you have a concern about a charge, we ask that you contact us directly before initiating a chargeback with your bank or card issuer. Most disputes can be resolved quickly through direct communication.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Initiating a chargeback or payment reversal without first contacting us constitutes a \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"breach of our Terms & Conditions\"}],\" (Section 11 — Prohibited Conduct). We reserve the right to contest chargebacks with documentation of order fulfilment and communications.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"In cases of confirmed fraud or genuine billing errors, we will cooperate fully with Razorpay Curlec and your financial institution to resolve the matter promptly.\"}]]}]]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"9. Pre-Order Payment Terms\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Pre-order payments are governed by Section 7 of our \",[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/terms\",\"className\":\"text-blue-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Terms & Conditions\"}],\". Key payment-specific provisions:\"]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Full payment is collected at the time of pre-order. We do not currently offer deposit or instalment arrangements.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"Buyer-initiated cancellations are eligible for a full refund within \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"14 days\"}],\" of placing the pre-order.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"After 14 days, pre-order payments are non-refundable on buyer-initiated cancellation, as procurement commitments will have been made.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"If we cancel the pre-order (discontinued item, sourcing failure), a \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white\",\"children\":\"full refund\"}],\" is issued within 7 business days.\"]}]]}]]}]]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\",\"children\":\"10. Contact\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"For all payment-related enquiries — including failed transactions, refund status, or billing discrepancies — contact us via our \",[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"text-blue-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Contact Us\"}],\" page. Please include your order reference number and a description of the issue.\"]}]}]]}]\n17:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-900 flex flex-wrap gap-6 justify-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/terms\",\"className\":\"text-blue-600 hover:text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Terms & Conditions\"}],[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/return-policy\",\"className\":\"text-blue-600 hover:text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Return & Refund Policy\"}],[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/privacy